    <sec id="sec2c">
      <title>Accuracy computation</title>
      <p>To compute accuracy we used the standard precision, recall and F-1 score measures: <disp-formula id="deqn01"><label>(1)</label><tex-math id="M17">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
